  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed replacement of the hipped roof on the existing garage with a flat roof profile, by reason of its siting in this open, visually prominent position and design, would result in a form of development that fails to respect the architectural composition of the host dwelling and would be detrimental to the character, appearance and visual amenities of the street scene and the setting of the Central Avenue, Hayes, Area of Special Local Character. The proposal therefore conflicts with Policies BE1 and HE1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan: Part One - Strategic Policies (November 2012) and Policies DMHB 1, DMHB 5, DMHB 11 and DMHB 12 of the Hillingdon Local Plan Part Two - Development Management Policies (January 2020).",
    "The existing front roof light, by reason of its siting, size and design, appears as an incongruous feature that fails to respect the architectural composition of the host dwelling and would be detrimental to the character, appearance and visual amenities of the street scene and the setting of the Central Avenue, Hayes, Area of Special Local Character. The proposal therefore conflicts with Policies BE1 and HE1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan: Part One - Strategic Policies (November 2012) and Policies DMHB 1, DMHB 5, DMHB 11 and DMHB 12 of the Hillingdon Local Plan Part Two - Development Management Policies (January 2020)."
